      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion rounds</strong> to a separate <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or pop them on the tray with the chips if you have space!) and drizzle them with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until softened and lightly golden</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1625659520802-x200.jpg",
