            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>finely chopped onion</strong>,<strong> lean</strong> <strong>beef mince</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong>,<strong> Henderson's Relish</strong>,<strong> beef stock mix</strong> and a good grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Mix together for 1-2 min or until really well combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide your <strong>lean beef mince mixture</strong> into shape them into 1 patty per person</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1625659525602-x200.jpg",
