          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger top your<strong> warmed brioche bun base </strong>with a squeeze of <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, a <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>, <strong>tomato slices</strong>, a <strong>cheesy lean beef patty</strong>, <strong>roasted onion round</strong> and the <strong>warmed brioche bun lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
